f cars, motorbikes and even caravans and motorhomes. He also writes features for other sections of the paper including travel and sport. Ironically for a motoring journalist he is also a passionate cyclist and runner.</p>","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/profile/martinlove","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/profile/martinlove","references":[]},{"id":"type/article","webTitle":"Article","type":"type","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/articles","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/type/article","references":[]},{"id":"publication/theobserver","webTitle":"The Observer","type":"publication","sectionId":"theobserver","sectionName":"From the Observer","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/theobserver/all","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/publication/theobserver","references":[]}],"references":[],"elements":[{"id":"gu-image-386023179","relation":"main","type":"image","assets":[{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Observer/Pix/pictures/2012/2/15/1329309913989/porsche-rs-bike-001.jpg","typeData":{"source":"PR","altText":"porsche rs bike","height":"54","credit":"PR","caption":"\"How many other Porsches are there which produce no emissions whatsoever?\": the high-spec, carbon-framed Porsche RS","width":"54"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Observer/Pix/pictures/2012/2/15/1329309915535/porsche-rs-bike-002.jpg","typeData":{"source":"PR","altText":"porsche rs bike","height":"130","credit":"PR","caption":"\"How many other Porsches are there which produce no emissions whatsoever?\": the high-spec, carbon-framed Porsche RS","width":"140"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Observer/Pix/pictures/2012/2/15/1329309916842/porsche-rs-bike-003.jpg","typeData":{"source":"PR","altText":"porsche rs bike","height":"84","credit":"PR","caption":"\"How many other Porsches are there which produce no emissio